OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist or fog patches
OL,6,Fsoon clearing to leave a largely dry
OL,7,Fday, albeit cloudier than on Tuesday,
OL,8,Fwith bright or sunny periods. Chance
OL,9,Fof a few showers breaking out into the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Staying mild, with light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers easing to give
OL,14,Fsome clear spells at first. A band of
OL,15,Frain will move southeastwards
OL,16,Fovernight, weakening as it does so. A
OL,17,Frelatively mild night. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
