OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy with some light rain
OL,6,For drizzle early morning, especially
OL,7,Fin Kent. Becoming dry with variable
OL,8,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells.
OL,9,FFeeling cooler compared to previous
OL,10,Fdays. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,13,Fwith an increasing likelihood of wet
OL,14,Fand windy conditions on Friday and
OL,15,Finto the weekend. Drier, brighter and
OL,16,Fwindy on Sunday. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
